message.content: The paper likely belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and question answering. Other possible sub-categories could include "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), "cs.DB" (Databases), "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), and "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as these areas are also relevant to the topic of knowledge graph based question answering.
